AKUPHAZAMISANGA isithunzi semiphumela yokuhlolwa kwabafundi baka-matric futhi akubanga namthelela, ukuputshuka kwamaphepha elemathematics nemayensi nyakenye. Lokhu kuvele embikweni wethimba, iNational Investigations Task Team, esithangamini soMnyango weMfundo eyisiSekelo nabezindaba izolo. UMnuz Hugh Amoore, owuSihlalo wethimba, uthe uphenyo luveze ukuthi bancane abafundi ababona lawa maphepha ngaphambi kokuthi abhalwe. “Kunobufakazi bokuthi iphepha leMaths kwabelwana ngalo emaqenjini angu-236 anabafundi abangu- 175 kwiWhatsApp, kanti angu- 62 okwabelwane ngalo kweleSayensi. Kodwa isibalo sincane kakhulu uma kuqhathaniswa nabangazange bawabone,” kusho u-Amoore Uthe amaphepha amaningi abebhekwe ngelokhozi ngesikhathi kumakwa kulawa maphepha aputshukile, akhombise ukuthi abafundi abaningi bebeziphendulela ngendlela yabo ngezimpendulo ezahlukene. Uthe labo bafundi abebesoleka ukuthi bawathola lawa maphepha okukholakala ukuthi bakulawo maqembu akwabelwana kuwo iphepha,  bebethola amamaki ahlukene ngesikhathi kuqhutshekwa nokumaka okwenza kungabi nobufakazi bokuthi bangena ephepheni sebelihlaziyile iphepha. Uthe bakhona abafundi abathole amamaki amahle kakhulu kulawa maphepha okudinga ukuthi kuphenywe kodwa wathi abekho kulawa maqembu okukholakala ukuthi lawa maphepha asatshalaliswa kuwo. Ecacisa uthe kubafundi abangu-175, babili kuphela abathole amamaki asolisayo kwele-maths. Uthe kuphinde kwabhekwa amamaki alaba bafundi abasolekayo emaphepheni okuqala alezi zifundo ezaputshuka kodwa kwatholakala ukuthi mncane kakhulu umehluko. Lolu phenyo luphinde lwaveza ukuthi zincane izikole okusolakala ukuthi zinabafundi ababona amaphepha ngaphambi kokuthi abhalwe. Uthe ngenxa yokuthi amaphepha aputshuka ngeWhatsApp, akulula ukuthola ukuthi asabalala kangakanani kodwa ubufakazi abanabo okwamanje bukhombisa ukuthi ukubhalwa kokuhlolelwa lezi zifundo, akuzange kube nomthelela omubi kangako ngakho mncane umonakalo owenzeka. Phakathi kwezincomo ezethulelwe umkhandlu oqinisekisa izingabunjalo lemiphumela uMalusi, ukuthi abafundi okusokala ukuthi baba nesandla ekusabalaliseni amaphepha aputshuka, bavalwe bangazitholi izitifiketi  zabo ngesikhathi kusaqhubeka uphenyo. Njengoba ngoFebhuwari 22, ozayo kuzokhishwa imiphumela ka-matric, laba bafundi bazothola izitatimende ezisuke zinemiphumela yabo njengoba izitifiketi ziphuza ukuphuma. Lezi zitatimende bazozilanda ezikoleni zabo ngoFebhuwari 23. Namhlanje uMalusi unesithangami nabezindaba lapho uzomemezela ukuthi uyakugunyaza ukukhishwa kwale miphumela. 